lead_paragraph: The fall of Michigan State could end up being the most dramatic in Big Ten football since the Gerald Ford-led Michigan Wolverines went from first to worst 82 years ago.

headline.print_headline: Spartans' Fall Could Be Big Ten's Biggest Since '34 Michigan
